{"tid":530572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[369]黃之鋒羅冠聰盼終院考慮公民抗命動機　周永康：希望律政司大步檻過","createTime":"2018-01-16T02:06:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-16T15:51:01.000Z","uid":51271,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5ed5d7f606fb9a23d3a7f50eb9c27a240217ebfb","tid":530572,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T02:06:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180116/s00001/1516067680376\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180116%2Fs00001%2F1516067680376&d=hhXIQQLhWnbAiN3mV1lGMU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=92d0b092\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180116%2Fs00001%2F1516067680376&h=89327c65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180116/s00001/1516067680376</a><br />\n<br />\n雙學三子黃之鋒、羅冠聰和周永康因2014年佔領運動前夕闖入政府總部東翼前地案件被改判監禁後提出上訴，終審法院今早開庭處理。黃之鋒、羅冠聰在法庭外表示，希望法庭判決時考慮公民抗命理念、珍視公民爭取民主的努力。<br />\n<br />\n羅冠聰表示，希望法庭伸張公義，把公民抗命理念考慮在判案中。他自言心情複雜，可能即時入獄，但認為非常重要的是上訴庭早前劃下了判決準則，即把行動者的動機完全不予考慮，但面對不民主體制時，市民應有更大權力用公民抗命方式向政府講「它錯了」，所以法庭應該考慮爭取民主的動機，期望法庭今天給予清晰而展示公義的答案。<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒說，今明兩天都各有一單案件可能面對即時判刑，是相當大挑戰，心情複雜。他同樣期望法庭就公民抗命的動機作清晰指引，這3年來香港社會有不少街頭運動，終院到底用什麼態度對待這些青年人和示威者，是相當關鍵的。他說希望自己明天是由街外走入法庭，非由囚車押解。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>周永康簡單地以「準備就緒」來形容自己目前的情況，又反過來說「希望律政司大步檻過」，「（捲入僭建風波的律政司長）鄭若驊『騰』過我哋」。他說，林鄭月娥曾說年輕人犯法就一定要面對懲罰，今天律政司長面對如此嚴峻考驗，他更想知道林鄭月娥如何回應，希望政府和律政司能解畫，釋除疑慮，「我祝律政司和林鄭月娥好運」。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f7e769009c305ed24de506f0caeed450de28375","tid":530572,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T04:46:16.000Z","msg":"又押後，上訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53cf150bd8625536ee7b63cc8283f60e8d8bec77","tid":530572,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T04:46:32.000Z","msg":"保釋"},{"pid":"a45b7fba7cb29b58cd76e292680a67f63baf3ce6","tid":530572,"uid":121393,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T15:10:19.000Z","msg":"點解呢三件垃圾仲未死"},{"pid":"437e8e45a6047d38132e9b834eaacb47f6ea8cfe","tid":530572,"uid":44358,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a45b7fba7cb29b58cd76e292680a67f63baf3ce6","tid":530572,"uid":121393,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T15:10:19.000Z","msg":"點解呢三件垃圾仲未死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T15:11:53.000Z","msg":"點解你老母咁老都做雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4460b88a2664187733d4c99d2b5bfa92c8200fc7","tid":530572,"uid":89683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T15:12:30.000Z","msg":"其實無限押後，究竟想點？"},{"pid":"5438f03faaef6f58d06353c12008366f68b347ca","tid":530572,"uid":121393,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T15:22:13.000Z","msg":"呢三件唯恐天下大亂嘅垃圾快d去死"},{"pid":"b878ed01282c9e436bfa5177f040e84e9909d434","tid":530572,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4460b88a2664187733d4c99d2b5bfa92c8200fc7","tid":530572,"uid":89683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T15:12:30.000Z","msg":"其實無限押後，究竟想點？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T15:51:01.000Z","msg":"押後左一次渣喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中嬸影響咁大一定慢慢研究架啦"}]}